des:
5 Stripe Daily will go live February 1st, 2018!!

5 Stripe Daily provides a daily update for everything Atlanta United to your Flash Briefing. We provide unofficial club updates on the following topics:

-Scores 
-Match Previews
-Roster Updates 
-Transfer News
-Club News 
-Fan Updates
-Standings
-MLS News

Wake Up to your favorite team every day, or go to bed knowing the hottest ATL UTD news!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
